title: SpaceX rocket launches from Florida carrying NASA planet-hunting telescope
text:
SpaceX rocket launches from Florida carrying NASA planet-hunting telescope 10:30am IST - 02:01 
A Falcon 9 rocket blasted off on Wednesday on SpaceX's first high-priority science mission for NASA, a planet-hunting space telescope whose launch was delayed for two days by a rocket-guidance glitch. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
